quran[399]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"UIbrâhîm wathi: “Myalezo mni na (lo) nize ngawo (apha) kanye kanye nina ziThunywa?”"
  51,32,"Zathi zona: “Inene thina sithunyelwe kubantu abazizaphula- mthetho"
  51,33,Ukuba sithulule phezu kwabo amatye odongwe
  51,34,Aphawulelwe abagabadeli phambi kweNkosi yakho.”
  51,35,Ngoko ke Sakhupha (wonke) olikholwa phakathi apho
  51,36,Kananjalo aSizanga Sifumane mntu ngaphandle komzi omnye wamaMuslim (umzi kaLût neentombi zakhe)
  51,37,Sashiya umqondiso apho kwabo basoyikayo isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  51,38,"Kananjalo kuMûsâ (kwakukho umnqondiso), ukumthumela kweThu kuFir’awn negunya elicacileyo"
  51,39,"Kodwa (uFir’awn) watshikila nabalandeli bakhe, wathi: “(UMûsâ) ngumenzi wemilingo nephambana.”"
  51,40,Samntywilisela elwandle yena namadoda omkhosi wakhe ngenxa yokuba wayesoleka
  51,41,"Nakuma’Ad (wabakhona umnqondiso), xa Sathumela umoya oludlolo1 (owavuthuzayo ngokuchaseneyo nabo)"
  51,42,"Awuzanga usindise nenye into owawubhudla phezu kwayo koko wayishiya itshabalele, ibubutyobo"
  51,43,"NakwaThamûd, xa kwathiwa kubo: “Yibani nizonwabisa okwethutyana.”"
  51,44,"Bona baba nendelelo ngokubhekiselele kumyalelo weNkosi yabo, ngoko iindudumo zabahlasela besajongile"
  51,45,"Azanga bakwazi ukuvuka ke, bengazanga bakwazi nokuzikhusela"
  51,46,"Kananjalo Satshabalalisa abantu bakwaNûh ngaphambili, inene, bona babengabantu, abagabadelayo"
  51,47,"Thina Sawabumba amazulu ngamandla. Inene, Thina Siyakwazi ukwandisa ukwandlaleka kwephakade"
  51,48,"Nomhlaba Siwandlalile, Hayi ubuncutshe boMlungiseleli (wendalo)"
  51,49,Kwizinto zonke Sidale amaqabane (azo) ngambini khona ukuze nikhumbule (iziBele zika-Allâh)
  51,50,Balekelani kuAllâh ke ngoko. Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi kuni ocacileyo
  51,51,Musani ukwayamanisa thixo wumbi kuAllâh. Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo kuni
  51,52,"Kwangokunjalo akuzanga khe kufike nawuphi na uMthunywa kwabangaphambili kunabo bangathi: “Umenzi wemilingo okanye iphambana.”"
  51,53,Ingaba babecetyiswe ngabo2 ukuba benze le nto? Nakanye bona buqu bangabantu abagabadela batsiba imida (ekungakholweni)
  51,54,Bayeke ke wena (Muhammad) kuba akuyi kusoleka. (njengoko uwuvakalisile umyalezo kubo)
  51,55,"Bakhumbuze kananjalo, kuba inene inkumbuzo ilulutho kumakholwa"
  51,56,Kananjalo aNdidalanga abantu neeJinni ngaphandle (kokubadalela) ukuba banqule Mna
  51,57,"Andinasixhaso Ndisifunayo kubo, Ndingafuni nakondliwa ngabo Mna"
  51,58,"Inene nguAllâh OnguMondli, uMninimandla amakhulu"
  51,59,Ke kaloku inene okwabo benza ubugwenxa sisabelo (sesohlwayo)esinjengesabelosabahlobobabo(abalandulelayo eli). MabangaNdiqhwayi ngokungenamonde ke
  51,60,Yeha ke kwabo bangakholwayo kwiMini abathenjiswe ngayo
  52,1,(Ndifunga ngeNtaba) yeTûr
  52,2,NangeNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  52,3,Kumacwecwe avulwe ondlalwa
  52,4,NangoMzi1 ohanjelwa rhoqo
  52,5,Nangophahla (izulu) oluphakamele phezulu
  52,6,Nangolwandle oluzele (ngumlilo)
  52,7,Inene isohlwayo seNkosi yakho siza kwenzeka
  52,8,Ngokuba akukho mthinteli (waso)
  52,9,NgeMini izulu liya kuzamazama ngokujikelezayo
  52,10,Neentaba zigqithe zimke
  52,11,Yeha ke ngalooMini kubaphiki
  52,12,Abancokola amampunge bezonwabisa
  52,13,Ngemini abaya kutshovelwa eMlilweni wesiHogo ngamandla
  52,14,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Nangu ke lo Mlilo naniwuphika"
  52,15,"Ngumlingo na lo, okanye aniboni"
  52,16,(Ngenani ke) nitshe phakathi apho; yibani nomonde okanye ningabi namonde kuyafana kuni. Nihlawulwa ngoko nakwenzayo kuphela
  52,17,Inene amalungisa aya kuba semiyezweni naselonwabeni
  52,18,"Esonwabela oko iNkosi yawo Iwanike kona, Ibe neNkosi yawo Iwakhusele esohlwayweni soMlilo wesiHogo"
  52,19,"(Kuya kuthiwa kwabakholwayo): “Yidlani, nisele, naneliseke ngenxa yoko nakwenzayo.”"
  52,20,"Baya kuba bengqiyamile ezitroneni ezidwelisiweyo, kananjalo Siya kubatshatisa neembelukazi zabafazi abanamehlo amakhulu (amahle)"
  52,21,"Abo baya bakholwa abantwana babo balandela ekhondweni labo ngokholo Siya kubadibanisa nenzala yabo, kwaye aSiyi kubabandeza nto kwizinto zabo. Umntu ngamnye awakusebenzelayo kugciniwe"
  52,22,Kananjalo Siya kubapha iziqhamo nenyama nantoni na abaya kuyinqwenela
  52,23,Baya kunikana indebe (yewayini) apho akuyi kubakho ntetho imbi nakwenziwa kwasono
  52,24,Kuya kuhamba hamba phakathi kwabo (izicaka) ezingamakhwenkwana azele ukulungiselela bona engathi ziiperile ezilondoloziweyo
  52,25,Ke kaloku baya kusondelana babuzane
  52,26,"Baya kuthi: “Inene thina kwixesha elidlulileyo esasikunye nabantu bakuthi ngalo sasisoyika (ukumenza umsindo uAllâh)"
  52,27,"Waza uAllâh Wasibonelela ngobuBele baKhe, Wasikhusela kananjalo kwisohlwayo soMlilo otshisayo"
  52,28,"Inene sasidla ngokucela kuYe ngaphambili. Inene, nguYe OnguMncedi, uSozinceba"
  52,29,Ngoko ke wena (Muhammad) khumbuza kuba wena ngoBabalo lweNkosi yakho akungosiyavumisa okanye umntu ophambeneyo
  52,30,"Okanye bathi (ngawe): “Yimbongi esilindele ukuba ihlelwe lilishwa lexesha”"
  52,31,"Yithi wena: “Lindani kaloku, kuba nam phakathi kwenu ndingomnye wabalindileyo!”"
  52,32,"Makube mhlawumbi ziingqondo zabo ezibayalela ukuba (batsho) obu (buxoki ngawe Muhammad), okanye (bona) bangabantu nje abagabadeleyo"
  52,33,"Okanye bathi: “Uyiqambe ngokwakhe (i’Kur’ân)”? Yeha bona abakholwa"
  52,34,Mabavelise isicengcelezo esifana nayo (i’Kur’ân) kaloku ukuba bathetha inyaniso
  52,35,Makube mhlawumbi badalwa ngento engekhoyo? Okanye ngabo abangabadali
  52,36,Makube mhlawumbi ngabo abadala amazulu nomhlaba? Nakanye abaqinisekanga
  52,37,"Makube mhlawumbi banoovimba (bobutyebi) beNkosi yakho, Okanye bangabalawuli babo (oovimba abo)"
  52,38,"Okanye banomchankcatho (wokuya ezulwini) abaphulaphula ngawo (iimfihlelo zezulu)? Ukuba kunnalo, umphulaphuli lowo wabo makaze nobungqina obucacileyo kaloku"
  52,39,Okanye Yena (uAllâh) Uneentombi nibe nina ninoonyana
  52,40,"Okanye wena (Muhammad), ubabiza intlawulo (ngalo myalezo) ukuze bazive besindekile ngumthwalo (wetyala lentlawulo)"
  52,41,"Okanye banolwazi lokungabonwayo, abalubhala phantsi"
  52,42,Okanye baqulunqa icebo? Kodwa abo bangakholwayo ngabo ekuqulunqwa ngabo
  52,43,OkanyebanomnyeuthixoongaphandlekoAllâh?Makazukiswe uAllâh Ongentla kwayo yonke into abayayamanisa naYe
  52,44,"Ke kaloku xa benokubona iceba lisiwa livela esibhakabhakeni bangathi: “Ngamafu (njee) ayinqumba!”"
  52,45,Bayeke ke wena bade badibane neMini yabo abaya kubethwa bengaqondi
  52,46,"Mini leyo icebo labo lingayi kubanceda nto, bengayi kuncedwa nakuncedwa"
  52,47,Inene kwabo benze ubugwenxa sisohlwayo esingaphambili kunoku kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi
  52,48,"Ke kaloku wena (Muhammad) yiba nomonde ngesigqibo senkosi yakho kuba inene wena usemehlweni eThu, kananjalo zukisa (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi, yakho xa uvuka"
  52,49,Nangenxalenye yobusuku Mzukise Yena nasemva (kokutshona) kweenkwenkwezi
  53,1,(Ndifunga) ngenkwenkwezi xa isihla
  53,2,Ugxa wenu (uMuhammad) akalahlekanga yaye akenzanga mpazamo
  53,3,Engathethi okomnqweno wakhe
  53,4,Asinto yimbi (le ‘Kur’ân) ngaphandle kokuba sisiTyhilelo esityhiliweyo
  53,5,Ufundiswe ngonamandla amakhulu (uJibrîl)
  53,6,"Ongenasiphene, yena waphakama waba ngemo yakhe yokwenene"
  53,7,Lo gama waye kwindawo ephakamileyo yolundi
  53,8,"Weza, wehla phantsi"
  53,9,Waba kumgama ongangobude bezaphetha ezibini okanye nganeno (kunoko)
  53,10,Watyhila (uJibrîl) kwisicaka saKhe (uAllâh) awakutyhilayo
  53,11,Intliziyo (ingqondo) ayizanga ixoke ngoko yakubonayo
  53,12,Niza kumphikisa na nina ngoko wakubonayo
  53,13,"Kananjalo\twambona\tyena\t(uMuhammad)\tngenene kwisihlandlo sesibini"
  53,14,NgakwiSidratul Muntaha
  53,15,"Kufutshane\tnayo\t(iSidratul\tMuntaha)\tkukho\tumyezo wokhuseleko (iPaladesi)"
  53,16,Yabona wathi usakugqunywa uMthi womLote yiloo nto yayiwugqumile
  53,17,Amehlo (OMprofeti uMuhammad) akalaqaza (ajonge kwenye indawo) engazanga agabadele
  53,18,Yena (wayibona ngenene eyona miqondiso mikhulu yeNkosi yakhe)
  53,19,Ke (nina) nibajongile na ooAl- Lat- noAl ‘Uzzâ
  53,20,"NoManât, ongowesithathu kubo"
  53,21,Ingaba okwenu ngabesiduna na ize kuYe ibe ngabesikhomokazi
  53,22,Oko ke (ukuba kunjalo) kukwaba okungenabulungisa
  53,23,"(Lawo) akanto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba ngamagama (njee) eniziqambele ngokwenu nina kunye nookhokho benu (magama lawo) uAllâh Angathumelanga gunya (ngawo) Abalandeli nto ngaphandle koqash-qash noko kunqwenelwa yimiphefumlo yabo, ukanti sele sifikile kubo isiKhokelo esivela eNkosini yabo"
  53,24,Ingaba umntu unako (konke) akunqwenelayo
  53,25,Kodwa uBomi belizayo bobuka-Allah nobokuqala
  53,26,Zingaphi iingelosi ezisezulwini ezintethelelo yazo ingayi kunceda nto ngaphandle kokuba uAllâh Ade Anike imvume kulowo Athande ukumnika namamkeleyo
  53,27,Inene abo bangakholwayo kuBomi oBuzayo bathiya iingelosi amagama esikhomokazi
  53,28,"Yaye malunga noko abanalwazi, akukho nto balandela yona ngaphandle koqash qash, inene, uqash-qash akancedi nto ngokuchasene nenyaniso"
  53,29,Wena zikhwebule kulowo utshikilela umyalezo weThu ongafuni nto ngaphandle kobomi beli hlabathi
  53,30,"Lowo ngumyinge wolwazi lwabo, inene iNkosi yakho yiYona, Yaziyo okokuba ngubani na olahlekileyo eNdleleni yaYo, ikwayiYo kananjalo Eyaziyo ukuba ngubani na okuso isiKhokelo"
  53,31,"Kananjalo kokuka-Allah okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni khon’ukuze Abuyekeze abo benza ukungcola (ngesohlwayo) ngoko bakwenzayo, Abuyekeze nabo benza okulungileyo (ngomvuzo) omhle"
  53,32,"Abo baziphephayo izono ezikhulu nezenzo ezingcolileyo, benze ezincinane kuphela, inene iNkosi yenu Iphangalele kuxolelo (lwezono), Yona Inazi kakuhle xa Inivelisa4 emhlabeni naxa naniizintsana ezibelekweni zoomama benu. Ngoko ke musani ukubanga ukuba ninyulu, Yena nguYena Waziyo ukuba ngubani na oMoyikayo"
  53,33,"Umbonile na lowo utshikileyo wafulathela, (i-Islam)"
  53,34,Waza wanikela kancinane waphinda wayeka
  53,35,"Ingaba unalo na ulwazi lokungabonwayo, ukuze abone"
  53,36,Akachazelwanga na ngokwakuseziBhalweni zikaMûsâ
  53,37,"NezikaIbrahim, owazalisekisayo"
  53,38,Akukho mthwali wamithwalo uya kuthwaliswa umthwalo womnye
  53,39,Kananjalo akukho nto umntu (aya kuyifumana) ngaphandle kwaleyo wayizabalazelayo
  53,40,Kwaye inene umzamo wakhe uza kubonwa
  53,41,Aze abuyekezwe ngawo ngembuyekezo egcweleyo
  53,42,Kananjalo eNkosini yakho kulapho isiphelo sikhoyo
  53,43,Inene yiYo (iNkosi yakho) Eyenza umntu ahleke aphinde alile
  53,44,IkwayiYo Eyenza ukufa Inike ubomi
  53,45,IkwayiYo Edala abalingane oyindoda nowasetyhini
  53,46,Ngeqabaza lembewu yomntu xa likhutshiwe
  53,47,Kuze (kube yimfuneko) kuYe (ukuba Adale) enye indalo
  53,48,NguYe kananjalo Otyebisayo5 Anelise
  53,49,Kananjalo nguYe iNkosi kaSirius
  53,50,Ukanti Yena Watshabalalisa abantu bokuqala bakwa’Ad
  53,51,NabakwaThamûd nabo Akazanga Abasindise
  53,52,Nabantu bakwaNûh ngaphambili. Inene yayingabo abaya ababi nabulungisa baba ngabacinezeli
  53,53,"Ke\tkaloku\tWazitshabalalisa\tizixeko\tezabhedululwayo Wazikhahlela phantsi"
  53,54,Wabagqumelela ngoko Wabagqumelela ngako
  53,55,ZiziphinakeezintsikelelozeNkosiyenuniyakuzithandabuza
  53,56,"Lo\t(Mprofeti)\tnguMlumkisi\tnjengabanye\tabaLumkisi bamandulo"
  53,57,IMini esondelayo isondele (yona)
  53,58,"Mayela\tnayo\takukho\tbani\tngaphandle\tkoAllâh Onokuyishenxisa"
  53,59,Ingaba le ntetho iyanimangalisa kusini na
  53,60,Ke kaloku nina niyahleka anilili
  53,61,Nibe nisadlalisa ngokuzonwabisa
  53,62,Qubudani ke nina (maMuslim) kuAllâh niMnqule. (Yena Yedwa)
  54,1,IYure sele ifikile yaye nenyanga sele icandeke (kubini)
  54,2,"Ke kaloku xa bebona umqondiso (ummangaliso), bayatshikila bathi: “(Lo) ngumlingo ogqithayo.”"
  54,3,"Kananjalo baye baphika, balandela iminqweno yabo. Kodwa into nganye inexesha lokufezekiswa (kwayo)"
  54,4,Ke kaloku sele ifikile kubo inkcazelo ekukho kuyo isilumkiso (esaneleyo ngokubhekiselele kugabadelo)
  54,5,Ubulumko obuphangaleleyo kodwa isilumkiso asibancedi (nto)
  54,6,"Bayeke ke (Muhammad), ngeMini uMkhwazi aya kubizela abantu kwinto engathandekiyo (uMlilo wesiHogo)"
  54,7,"Amehlo abo aya kuba ethobekile, baya kuphuma emangcwabeni wabo bengathi ziinkumbi bethe saa"
  54,8,"Begxalathelana besiya phambili kuMkhwazi. Abangakholwayo baya kuthi: “Le yiMini enzima.”"
  54,9,"Abantu bakaNûh baphika ngaphambili kunabo, ke kaloku basiphika isiCaka seThu. Bathi: “ (Lo uNûh) yindoda ephambanayo” wada (uNûh) wagxothwa (ngabo)"
  54,10,"Ke kaloko wacela eNkosini yakhe: “Inene mna ndoyisakele, ndincede ke Wena (Nkosi yam).”"
  54,11,Thina ke Savula iingcango zezulu nemvula eyathululeka phantsi
  54,12,"Eyenza umhlaba wagqabhuka yimithombo namanzi, aza namanzi adibana nento eyayisele imiselwe kakade"
  54,13,Samthumela ke yena (ngenqanawa eyenziwe) ngamaplanga nezikhonkwane
  54,14,Idada phantsi kolondolozo lweThu njengomvuzo kulowo wayephikiwe (uNûh)
  54,15,"Sayishiya\tukuba\tibe\tngumqondiso1,\tukhona\tke\toza kukhumbula (okanye afumane isilumkiso)"
  54,16,Saba njani ke ukuba (buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,17,"Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,18,Ama’Ad aphika; saba njani ke (ukuba buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,19,"Inene, Thina Sathumela kubo umoya otswinayo ngemini eyayiyeyeshwangusha (elalisihla emva kweshwangusha)"
  54,20,Lincothula abantu ngokungathi zizibhukubhuku zemithi yesundu encothulwe neengcambu
  54,21,Saba njani (ukuba buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,22,"Kananjalo Siyenze yalula i’Kur’ân ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,23,AmaThamûd asala isilumkiso
  54,24,"Athi:“Ingabangumntuomnyephakathikwethuesizakulandela yena? Inene singaba sekulahlekeni nasempambanweni"
  54,25,Ingaba umyalezo uthunyelwe kuye phakathi kwethu? Hayi khona lixoki elingenazintloni (lo)!”
  54,26,"Baza\tkumazi\tngomso\tukuba\tngubani\tna\tolixoki elingenazintloni"
  54,27,"Inene Thina Sithumele ithokazi lenkamela ukuba libe luvavanyo kubo, bajonge ke ube nomonde"
  54,28,"Ubaxelele kananjalo okokuba amanzi baza kwahlulelana ngawo, (Nenkamela), ngenye (imini) kuza kusela bona (ize ibe yinkamela ngenye imini)"
  54,29,"Kodwa bona babiza ugxa wabo2, waba nesibindi wayinqumla imisipha"
  54,30,Saba njani ke (ukuba buhlungu) iSohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,31,Inene Thina Sathoba isiqhushumbisi phezu kwabo baba ngathi ziintsasa ezomileyo ezizizijungqu zesibaya sezilwanyana
  54,32,"Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,33,Abantu bakwaLût basala isilumkiso
  54,34,"Inene, Thina Sathumela isiphango samatye phezu kwabo ngaphandle kosapho lukaLût, lona Salusindisa phambi koms’obomvu"
  54,35,NgoBabalo oluvela kuThi. Simvuza kanjalo ke onombulelo
  54,36,"Ke kaloku yena wayesele ebalumkisile (kwantlandlolo) ngohlaselo lweThu, kodwa bona basiphikisa isilumkiso"
  54,37,"Kananjalo bafuna ukuxhwila iindwendwe zakhe, Kodwa Sabamfamekisela amehlo abo (SiSithi): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,38,Ke kaloku ekuseni bafikelwa sisohlwayo esibuhlungu
  54,39,"(Kwathiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,40,Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke kodwa ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula
  54,41,Kanti nakubantu bakwaFir’awn kwafika isilumkiso
  54,42,"Bayala imiqondiso yeThu yonke, Sabahlasela ke ngohlaselo lwaloWo Unobunganga, Unamandla"
  54,43,"Ingaba (abantu) abangakholwayo benu bangcono kunabayaa bamandulo, okanye ninogonyo oluvela kwiziBhalo"
  54,44,"Okanye bathi: “Thina silibandla elixhasanayo,” kusini na"
  54,45,"(Elo) bandlana labo liza koyiswa, kwaye baza kuza ngemiva (babaleke)"
  54,46,"Kodwa iYure lixesha labo elimisiweyo, kwaye iYure leyo ingaphaya ngokonakalisa yaye ikrakra ngakumbi"
  54,47,Inene izaphula-mthetho zisekulahlekeni nasempambanweni
  54,48,"NgeMini abaya kurhuqelwa eMlilweni ngobuso babo kuya (kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani ukuchukunyiswa sisiHogo kaloku”"
  54,49,Inene Sidale zonke izinto ngommiselo (wento eziya kuba yiyo)
  54,50,"Ukanti\tumyalelo\tweThu\tuba\tmnye\tjwi\tube\tngathi kukuqhwanyaza kweliso"
  54,51,"Kananjalo Sele Sabatshabalalisa abanjengani, ukhona phofu za kukhumbula"
  54,52,Kananjalo yonke into abayenzayo ibhaliwe emacwecweni
  54,53,Kwaye nto nganye encinane (nenkulu) ibhaliwe
  54,54,Inene amalungisa aya kuba phakathi kwemiyezo nemilambo
  54,55,"Esihlalweni sentlonipheko ecaleni kukaSobunganga, uSomandla"
  55,1,USolubabalo
  55,2,Wafundisa i’Kur’ân
  55,3,Wadala umntu
  55,4,Wamfundisa ukuthetha
  55,5,"Ilanga\tnenyanga\tzijikeleza\tngokwemilinganiselo echanekileyo (ezibalelwe yona)"
  55,6,Neenkwenkwezi nemithi ziyaqubuda
  55,7,Nezulu Waliphakamisa walinyanzela ukuzinza
  55,8,Khon’ukuze ningayigabadeli imida ebekiweyo
  55,9,Kwanokuba nijongisise nimete (izinto) ngokulinganayo ningenzi umlinganiselo ube nesikhwasilima
  55,10,"Kanti\tnomhlaba\tUwubeke\tphantsi\t(Wawandlalela) izilwanyana"
  55,11,"Apho kuwo kukho iziqhamo, iidatilisi zesundu ezivelisa amakhasi"
  55,12,"neenkozo kananjalo ezinamagqabi efula, nezityalo ezinuka kamnandi"
  55,13,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,14,Wadala umntu ngodongwe lokwenyani olunjengodongwe lomxonxi
  55,15,Ukanti zona iijinni Wazidala ngedangatya lomlilo ongenamsi
  55,16,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,17,"(Yena) yiNkosi yazo zombini iiMpumalanga, EkwayiNkosi yazo zombini iiNtshonalanga"
  55,18,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,19,Yena Wakhulula iilwandle ezimbini1 ukuba zidibane
  55,20,"Phakathi kwazo kukho umsantsa, alukho olutsiba umda kuwo (ezi lwandle zimbini)"
  55,21,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,22,Kuzo zombini (ezi lwandle) kuphuma iiperile neekorale
  55,23,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,24,Kananjalo zezaKhe iinqanawa eziye (zibonakale) ziphakamile elwandle ngathi ziintaba
  55,25,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,26,Wonke ubani kuwo (umhlaba) uza kutshabalala
  55,27,Kuze kusale uBuso2 beNkosi yakho uMnini bungangamsha nozuko
  55,28,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,29,"Wonke osemazulwini nasemhlabeni ucela kuYe; imihla yonke, Yena Uba nento Akuyo (Ayenzayo)"
  55,30,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,31,"Siza\tkunihoya\tnina\tzidalwa\tzibini\t(iiJinni\tnabantu) zixhomekeke (kuThi)"
  55,32,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,33,"Hini na bandla ndini leejinni nabantu, ukuba niye naba nako ukugqitha ngaphaya kwemimandla yezulu nomhlaba gqithani ke. Aniyi kugqitha ngaphandle kwegunya (elivela kuAllâh)"
  55,34,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,35,Kuya kuthunyelwa kuni amadangatya omlilo nomsi yaye aniyi kuzikhusela
  55,36,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,37,"Ke kaloku lakucandeka izulu, livuleke, libe ngathi yirozi ebomvu okwe-oli"
  55,38,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,39,Ngaloo Mini akukho namnye oza kubuzwa ngesono sakhe phakathi koluntu neejinni (kuba abenzi bezono nabalungileyo baya kuzicacela ngaloo Mini)
  55,40,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,41,"Izaphula-mthetho ziya kubonakala ngeempawu zazo, yaye ziya kuxhakamfulwa ngeenyawo (zazo)"
  55,42,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,43,Nasi ke isiHogo ebesiphikwa zizaphula-mthetho
  55,44,Baya kujikeleza phakathi kwaso namanzi atshisayo enziwe ashushu (kanobom)
  55,45,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,46,"Ke yena lowo waye woyika ukumiswa (phambi) kweNkosi yakhe, uya kuba neMiyezo emibini"
  55,47,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,48,(IMiyezo le yo) iya kuba namasebe (athe saa)
  55,49,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,50,Kuyo yomibini (iMiyezo leyo) kuya kubakho imithombo empompozayo
  55,51,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,52,Kuyo yomibini kuya kubakho zonke iziqhamo zeentlobo ezimbini
  55,53,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,54,"Bengqengqe kwiimandlalo zabo eziqukunjelwe ngesilika enzima, iziqhamo zemiyezo emibini zona zijingela phantsi (kufutshane)"
  55,55,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,56,"(Kuloo miyezo) kuya kubakho abafazi abaya kuba bekrwaqula ngokuzibambileyo, abangazanga bachukunyiswe ndoda najinni ngaphambili"
  55,57,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,58,Ngokungengathi ziiRubhi neekorale
  55,59,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,60,Ingaba ukhona na umvuzo wokulungileyo ngaphezulu kokulungileyo na
  55,61,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,62,Ngezantsi kwayo yomibini (iMiyezo leyo) kuya kubakho eminye iMiyezo emibini
  55,63,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,64,Iya kuba luhlaza yaka (ngokwebala)
  55,65,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,66,Kuyo yomibini kuya kubakho imithombo emibini etsawulayo
  55,67,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,68,Kuyo yomibini kuya kubakho iziqhamo nemithi yesundu nerharnathi
  55,69,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,70,"Kuyo kuya kubakho abafazi abalungileyo, abahle"
  55,71,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,72,"Abaziimbelukazi\teziya\tkujezula\tngokuzibambileyo, eminqubeni emihle"
  55,73,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,74,Ezingazanga zachukunyiswa ngumntu najinni ngaphambili
  55,75,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,76,Zithe zava kwizihlalo ezitofotofo eziluhlaza neenkukho ezintle
  55,77,Ziziphi na ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,78,"Lisikelelekile igama leNkosi yakho, uMnini bungangamsha nozuko"
  56,1,Xa isehlo sisihla
  56,2,Ekuhleni kwaso akukho kuphika
  56,3,Siya kuthobisela abanye sinyusele abanye
  56,4,Xa umhlaba ushukuma ngokudlokova
  56,5,Neentaba zidiliziwe zaluthuli
  56,6,Zaba luthuli oluphaphathekayo
  56,7,Nize nina nibe ziindidi ezintathu
  56,8,Ke kaloku amadlelane angasekunene; ziintoni na amadlelane angasekunene
  56,9,"Namadlelane\tangasekhohlo;\tziintoni\tna\tamadlelane angasekhohlo"
  56,10,Nabanduleli; abanduleli (bona)
  56,11,Abo ngabo basondezwe kufutshane (noAllâh)
  56,12,EMiyezweni yolonwabo
  56,13,Neqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamandulo
  56,14,Nabambalwa (bezizukulwana) zamva
  56,15,(Baya kuba) sezitroneni eziqukunjelwe (ngezihombiso)
  56,16,"Behleli zava kuzo, bejongene ubuso ngobuso"
  56,17,Kuya kujikeleza phakathi kwabo amakhwenkwe enzelwe (ukuphila) ngonaphakade
  56,18,"Nezitya, imiphanda nendebe (yewayini) ephuma kumthombo ompompozayo"
  56,19,"Akukho kuqaqamba kwantloko baya kuba nako apho, bengayi kunxila nakunxila"
  56,20,Neziqhamo baya kuzikhethela
  56,21,Nenyama yentaka abathe bayinqwenela
  56,22,Neembelukazi (zabafazi) abanamehlo abanzi (amahle)
  56,23,Abafana neeperile ezilondolozwe ngononophelo
  56,24,Njengomvuzo woko bakusebenzelayo
  56,25,Abayi kuva ntetho ingcolileyo nakwenziwa kwasono apho
  56,26,"Kuphela (abaya kukuva) iya kuba: “(Makube) luxolo.”"
  56,27,"Amadlelane\tangasekunene;\tyintoni\tamadlelane angasekunene"
  56,28,"(Baya kuba) phakathi kwemithi yoMlote, engenameva"
  56,29,Nemithi yebhanana (eneziqhamo) ezalekeneyo
  56,30,Nomthuzi owandisiweyo
  56,31,Namanzi ampompozayo
  56,32,Neziqhamo ezininzi
  56,33,Ezinganqamkiyo (ukuntshula) zingalelwanga nokwalelwa (ukuba zityiwe)
  56,34,Nakwiimandlalo eziphakanyiselwe phezulu
  56,35,Inene Thina Sibavelisele (abafazi bePaladesi) kwindalo (entsha)
  56,36,Sabenza baziintombi (ezingazani nandoda)
  56,37,Ezizinikeleyo (kubayeni bazo) zinobudala obulinganayo
  56,38,Izezamadlelane angasekunene
  56,39,Aliqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamandulo
  56,40,Neqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamva
  56,41,Neqela lamadlelane angasekhohlo yintoni na amadlelane angasekhohlo
  56,42,"(Baya\tkuba)\tseMlilweni\totshisayo\tnamanzi\tashushu (kanobom)"
  56,43,Nethinzi lomsi omnyama thsuh
  56,44,Elingapholanga lingancedi nakunceda
  56,45,Inene bona kaloku bazanelisa ngobutyebi ngaphambili
  56,46,Kananjalo bona babethe gqolo ngokugabadela (ngezono ezikhulu)
  56,47,"Kwaye babesithi: “Xa sele sifile saba luthuli namathambo, siza kuphinda ngenene sivuswe"
  56,48,Nookhokho bethu nabo ngokunjalo?”
  56,49,"Yithi wena (Muhammad): “Inene abantu bokuqala nabantu bokugqibela"
  56,50,Baza kuqokelelelwa iMini ekhethiweyo.”
  56,51,Ke kaloku nina ndawonye nabo balahlekileyo baphikayo
  56,52,Niya kutyiswa umthi weZa’kkûm
  56,53,Nizalise izisu zenu ngawo
  56,54,Niphinde ngaphezu koko nisezwe amanzi atshisayo
  56,55,Kwaye niya kusela ukusela kweenkamela ezinxaniweyo
  56,56,Iya kuba bububele babo (abaza kubenzelwa) ngoMhla woVuko
  56,57,"Sinidalile nje, kungani na ukuba ningakholwa"
  56,58,Nikubonile phofu oko niye nikukhuphe
  56,59,Nini na abakudalayo nokuba siThi abanguMdali
  56,60,"Simisele ukufa phakathi kwenu, yaye Thina ngeKhe Soyiswe"
  56,61,Kangangokuba Siya kuyiguqula imbonakalo yenu Sinivelise ngenye imo eningayaziyo nina
  56,62,"Ke kaloku sele niyazi indalo yokuqala, aniyi kukhumbula ke"
  56,63,Niyibonile phofu (imbewu) leyo niyityalayo
  56,64,Nini na abayenza ikhule nokuba Sithi abakhulisi
  56,65,Ukuba beSinokuthanda beSingasuka Siyenze yome ibe bubutyobo nihlale nimangazekile
  56,66,"(Nithi): “Inene thina (ngoku) sisematyaleni"
  56,67,Thina sibandazelekile.”
  56,68,Niwabonile phofu amanzi lawo niwaselayo?”
  56,69,Nini na abaza nawo emafini nokuba SiThi abawathobayo
  56,70,"Ukuba beSithanda beSingasuka Siwenze akrakre, kungokuba kutheni ukuba ningabi nambulelo (kuAllâh)"
  56,71,Niwujongile phofu umlilo lowo niwulumekayo
  56,72,Nini na abavelisa umthi wawo nokuba SiThi abaVelisi (bawo)
  56,73,Siwenze wasisikhumbuzi (soMlilo wesiHogo) nembonelelo yabahambi
  56,74,Ngoko ke zukisa igama leNkosi yakho uMnini bukhulu
  56,75,Ke kaloku Mna Ndifunga ngokutshona kweenkwenkwezi
  56,76,Inene esi sisifungo ukuba beniMazi (uMnini) bukhulu
  56,77,Inene yona (le) yi’Kur’ân eZukileyo
  56,78,EseNcwadini ekhuselekileyo
  56,79,"Akukho\tnamnye\toyichukumisayo\tngaphandle kwabahlambulukileyo"
  56,80,IsisiTyhilelo esivela eNkosini yamaphakade
  56,81,Ingaba yintetho eloo lohlobo (le ‘Kur’ân) na le niyiphikayo (nina bangakholwayo)
  56,82,Endaweni (yokubulela uAllâh) ngembonelelo Aninika yona niyaMphika nina
  56,83,Kutheni xa umphefumlo (womntu ofayo) ufikelela emqaleni (ningangeneleli) kaloku
  56,84,Ukusuka apho nina ngeloo lixa (nisuka nime) nijonge
  56,85,Thina ke Siba Sikufutshane kuye kunani kodwa nina nibe ningaboni
  56,86,Kutheni kaloku (nisima nijonge ningamncedi nje) xa ngaba anizozicaka (kuThi)
  56,87,Ningambuyiseli nje (ebomini kwakhona) ukuba ninenyaniso
  56,88,Ke kaloku ukuba yena (umfi lowo) ube engomnye wabo basondeleyo kuAllâh (ngokuthandwa)
  56,89,"Okwakhe\tiya\tkuba\tkukuphumla\t(ngoxolo)\tnoBubele noMyezo wolonwabo"
  56,90,Kanti ukuba ube engomnye wamadlelane wabangasekunene
  56,91,"(Iingelosi ziya kuthi kuye): “Makube lukhuseleko noxolo kuwe wena oluvela kumadlelane angasekunene.”"
  56,92,"Kodwa ukuba ube engomnye wabaphiki, abalahlekileyo"
  56,93,Okwakhe lowo kukubelezelelwa ngamanzi atshisayo
  56,94,Nokutsha eMlilweni wesiHogo
  56,95,Inene le yinyaniso yoqobo
  56,96,"Zukisa igama leNkosi yakho, uMnini bungangamsha"
  57,1,"Yonke into esemazulwini nasemhlabeni izukisa uAllâh, Yena nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  57,2,"LolwaKhe ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba, Unika ubomi, Enze ukufa. Kananjalo Yena Unamandla ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"
  57,3,"Yena ngowokuQala ngowokuGqibela, Ungentla, yaye Ukufutshane, kananjalo nguMazi wezinto zonke"
  57,4,"NguYe Owadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeentsuku ezintandathu, waza Wanyukela ngentla kweTrone, Uyakwazi okungena emhlabeni nokuphuma kuwo, nokuhlayo kuvela ezulwini nokunyukela kulo kwaye Yena Ukunye nani naphi na apho nikhoyo, kananjalo uAllâh Uyakwazi enikwenzayo"
  57,5,Yena lulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba. Kananjalo kukuAllâh apho (zonke) izinto zibuyela khona
  57,6,"Yena Wenza ubusuku bungene kwimini, Enze imini ingene kubusuku, Yaye nguMazi wokusezifubeni"
  57,7,"Kholwani ke kuAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, ninikele kumalizo ngoko Anenze naba ziindlalifa zako. Ngokuba abo bakholiweyo phakathi kwenu baze banikele kumalizo baya kuba nomvuzo omkhulu"
  57,8,"Kungani na ukuba ningakholwa kuAllâh lo gama uMthunywa enimemela ekukholweni kwiNkosi yenu, ethe kananjalo wathabatha umnqophiso wenu, ukuba ninokuthi nikholwe"
  57,9,"NguYe Othumele iiVesi kwisiCaka saKhe (uMuhammad) ezibubungqina obucacileyo khona ukuze anikhuphe ebumnyameni anifake ekukhanyeni. Inene uAllâh Unobubele, Unenceba kuni"
  57,10,"Kungani na ukuba ninganikeli eNdleleni ka-Allâh lo gama ilifa lamazulu nomhlaba ilelaKhe? Abalingani phakathi kwenu abo banikelayo, balwa nokulwa ngaphambi (koloyiso lwaseMakkah) nabo balwayo (emva kwalo). Abo (balwa ngaphambili) bangentla ngokwebakala kunabo banikela kamva balwa nokulwa. Kodwa uAllâh bonke Ubathembise (ngomvuzo). Kananjalo uAllâh enikwenzayo Uyakwazi"
  57,11,Ngubani (kuni) oya kuboleka uAllâh imboleko elungileyo khon’ukuze (Ayihlawule kuye) ngokuphindaphindiweyo aze ngaphezu koko abe nomvuzo oxabisekileyo
  57,12,"NgeMini eniya kuwabona amakholwa namakholwakazi, ukukhanya kwawo kuwakhokelele ngaphambi kwawo nangasekunene kwawo, (kuya kuthiwa): “Iindaba zovuyo kuni namhlanje zezeMiyezo ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo, niya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade Inenene le yimpumelelo enkulu!”"
  57,13,"NgeMini leyo abahanahanisi nabahanahanisikazi baya kuthi kwabo bakholwayo, “Khanisilindeni khon’ukuze sizuze inxalenye yokukhanya kwenu.” Kuya kuthiwa kubo: “Buyelani emva kwenu niye kufuna ukukhanya.” Ke kaloku udonga luya kubekwa phakathi kwabo lunocango, umphakathi walo unenceba, kodwa umphandle walo usisohlwayo"
  57,14,"Bona (abahanahanisi) baya kukhwaza (abakholwayo) bathi: “Sasingekunyanga nani na?” Abakholwayo baya kuthi: “Ewe, kodwa nina nazithuthumbisa ngokwenu, nilindele (ilishwa phezu kwethu1) neengcinga zeminqweno yenu zanimfamekisa kwada kwafika umyalelo ka-Allâh. Kwaye umkhohlisi (uSathana) wanikhohlisa ngoAllâh"
  57,15,"Namhlanje ke akukho ntlawuliso yakuzikhulula iya kwamkelwa kuni nakwabo bangakholwayo. Ikhaya lenu nguMlilo, yiyona nto inifanele kakhulu (leyo). Aliselibi ngako ikhaya lenu lokugqibela"
  57,16,"Alikafiki na ixesha kwabo bakholwayo lokuba iintliziyo zabo zibe nokuzithoba, zizinikele kwinkumbulo ka-Allâh noko kwehlayo kuyinyaniso (i’Kur’ân)? IsiBhalo ngaphambili, kwaza kwathi kwakugqitha ithuba elide kubo iintliziyo zabo (zaqaqadeka) zaba lukhuni, ukanti uninzi lwabo bayadelela, abanantobeko"
  57,17,Yazini into yokuba uAllâh Unika ubomi emhlabeni emva kokungabi nabomi kwawo. Sinicacisele kakuhle imiqondiso hleze niqiqe
  57,18,"Inene amadoda anikelayo ngamalizo, nabasetyhini abanikelayo ngamalizo baboleke uAllâh imboleko elungileyo, iya (kuhlawulwa) ngokuphindeneyo kubo kananjalo baya kuba nomvuzo oxabisekileyo"
  57,19,"Abo bakholwayo kuAllâh nabaThunywa baKhe abo bangabaxhasi benyaniso nabafelukholo, bakunye neNkosi yabo. Okwabo ngumvuzo wabo nokukhanya kwabo kodwa bona abo bangakholwayo, baphika iiVesi zeThu, abo ngamadlelane oMlilo wesiHogo"
  57,20,"Kwazini kananjalo okokuba ubomi balo mhlaba yintlekisa njee nesiphambukisi nobunewunewu nokuqhayiselana nokhuphiswano ekwandiseni ubutyebi nabantwana njengomzekelo wemvula ezityalo zayo zikhula zigcobise umhlwayeli, zisuke zome, ubone sele zijike zamthubi; zisuke zibe bubutyobo obuthe saa. Kanti ke kuBomi oBuzayo sisohlwayo esibuhlungu noxolelo oluvela kuAllâh nokwamkeleka. Buyintoni ubomi basemhlabeni ngaphandle kokuba kukuziqhatha"
  57,21,"Khuphisanani ke ngokufuna ukuxolelwa yiNkosi yenu nomyezo obubanzi bawo bungangobubanzi bamazulu nomhlaba, ulungiselelwe abo bakholwayo kuAllâh nabaThunywa baKhe. Obo bubuBele buka-Allâh Abunika lowo Athande ukumnika, kwaye uAllâh nguMnini buBele oMkhulu"
  57,22,Akukhontlekeleihlayoemhlabeniokanyekuniingabhalwanga phambi kokuba ibekho Inene oko kulula kuAllâh
  57,23,"Khon’ukuze\tningalahli\tithemba\tngoko kuniphosileyo ningakhukhumali kananjalo ngoko Aninike kona. Kwaye uAllâh Akamthandi wonke ozingcayo, noqhayisayo"
  57,24,"(Abo) bangamagogotya bayalela ubugogotya (kwabanye) ke kaloku lowo utshikilayo, inene uAllâh Akananto Ayidingayo, nguSokudunyiswa"
  57,25,"Sele Sabathumela abaThunywa beThu nemiqondiso ecacileyo Sathumela neziBhalo kubo nendlela yokugweba khona ukuze abantu bahlale besebulungiseni. Kananjalo Sathumela2 intsimbi ekukho amandla amakhulu emikhosi kuyo (nezinye izinto) eziyinzuzo eluntwini khon’ukuze uAllâh Enze bacace abo baMxhasayo neziThunywa zaKhe ezingabonwayo. Inene uAllâh Unamandla, Unobunganga"
  57,26,"Kananjalo Sele Sathumela uNûh noIbrâhîm Saza kananjalo Sabeka ubuProfeti neziBhalo kwinzala yabo; yaye phakathi kwayo (inzala yabo leyo) kukho lowo ukhokelelekileyo, kodwa uninzi lwabo alunantobeko konke konke"
  57,27,"Ke kaloku ezinyaweni zabo Sathumela abaThunywa beThu Sabalandelisa ngo’Isâ, unyana kaMaryam, Samnika iVangeli Safaka imfobe nenceba ezintliziyweni zabo balandela yena nokungatshati (ukungatshati) oko baziqambela ngokwabo, Asizanga Sibayalele ngako ngaphandle (kokuzenzela ngokwabo) befuna ukwamkeleka kwako (ukungatshati oko) kuAllâh. Kodwa (ukungatshati oko) azanga bakugcine ngendlela efanelekileyo. Thina ke Sanika abo bakholwayo phakathi kwabo umvuzo wabo kodwa uninzi lwabo alunantobeko konke-konke"
  57,28,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, yoyikani uAllâh nikholwe nakuMthunywa waKhe: Yena Uya kuninika isahlulo esiphindwe kabini kwinceba yaKhe. Anenzele ukukhanya eniya kuhamba ngako Anixolele futhi, ke kaloku uAllâh nguMxoleli, nguSozinceba"
  57,29,(Oku kunjalo) khon’ukuze aBantu beNcwadi (amaYuda namaKhristu) bazi okokuba abanamandla ngokuchasene noBabaloluka-AllâhkwanokubabonkeubuBelebuseSandleni saKhe; Ubunika lowo Athande ukumnika kananjalo uAllâh nguMnini buBele Omkhulu